This is the changelog for FASTX::Abi. Version prior to v 0.1 are preliminary (alpha) release, not to be used in production.

0.05	2019-05-20
	* POD updates

0.03	2019-05-15
	* *NEW* _new()_ has attribute 'keep_abi' to preserve chromas object, otherwise deleted (_get_trace_info()_ changed accordingly)
	* _new()_ now validates input attributes and die if unexpected value is passed
	* New unit tests
	* *TODO* validate object attributes populated by _new()_ 

0.02	2019-05-14
	* *FIXED* release test (version) was pointing to wrong module
	* Update POD
	* Added unit tests
	* Added GitHub repository
	* Added TravisCI testing

0.01	2019-05-12
	* Initial release (alpha)
